<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
  <title>글 작성</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body class="app-page">
<div class="app-shell">
  <div class="top-card">
    <div>
      <div class="small-label">작성자</div>
      <h1 class="page-title"><%= studentName %></h1>
      <div class="meta-line"><%= studentClass ? "분반: " + studentClass : "" %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="timer-box">
      남은 시간 <strong id="timerText">--:--</strong>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel-card">
    <h2 class="section-title">주제</h2>
    <div class="topic-box"><%= topic %></div>

    <div class="notice-inline">
      <strong>유의사항</strong>
      <div>• 복사 및 붙여넣기 불가 / • 화면 이탈 시 입력 불가 / • 교수자 승인 후 작성 가능</div>
    </div>

    <div class="count-box">
      공백 포함 <strong><span id="withSpace">0</span></strong> /
      공백 제외 <strong><span id="withoutSpace">0</span></strong> /
      최소 글자수 <strong><%= minChars %></strong>
    </div>

    <div id="lockBanner" class="lock-banner" style="display:none;">
      입력창이 차단되었습니다. 교수자 승인 후 다시 작성할 수 있습니다.
    </div>

    <textarea id="editor"><%= text %></textarea>

    <div class="action-row">
      <button type="button" class="soft-btn" onclick="manualSave()">임시저장</button>
      <button type="button" class="danger-btn" id="submitBtn" onclick="submitExam()">제출</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="modalOverlay" class="modal-overlay" style="display:none;">
  <div class="modal-card">
    <h3 id="modalTitle">알림</h3>
    <p id="modalMessage"></p>
    <div id="modalButtons" class="modal-buttons"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  const id = "<%= id %>"
  const minChars = <%= minChars %>
  const startTime = <%= startTime ? startTime : "null" %>
  const endTime = <%= endTime ? endTime : "null" %>
  const started = <%= started ? "true" : "false" %>
  const initialLocked = <%= locked ? "true" : "false" %>
</script>
<script src="/editor.js"></script>

<script>

document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded",()=>{

  const elem=document.documentElement

  if(elem.requestFullscreen){
    elem.requestFullscreen()
  }

})

</script>




</body>
</html>